# Web UI

- **Stack:** HTML + CSS + JS, no build step.
- **Modules:** `api.js` (fetch), `ratings.js` (spectrum bars), `render-beach.js` (detail HTML), page controller per route.
- **CSS:** Single `web/css/ocean.css` — tokens, layout, components, page sections.
- **Lazy load:** Index JSON first, detail JSON on user action.
- **No frameworks** unless user requests React/etc.

Keep pages thin — logic in `web/js/`, markup in `web/*.html`.
